      "content": "thanks for the ideas. i'm looking at the maintenance log now too and it says the 17th is actually when they're pulling the plug on the H100 nodes entirely—meaning they aren't just going offline for a bit, they're being decommissioned for good. given that, how does that change your optimization plan? we can't really migrate much if the hardware is being physically removed.",
